Package hr.dice.assignments.currency_exchange.dto

Class ConvertAmountResponseDto

java.lang.Object
hr.dice.assignments.currency_exchange.dto.ConvertAmountResponseDto
public class ConvertAmountResponseDto extends Object
Data transfer object (DTO) representing the response for converting an amount from one currency to another.
